{"title_page": "RK Vogo\u0161\u0107a", "text_new": "{{multiple issues|\n{{primary sources|date=April 2017}}\n{{No footnotes|date=April 2017}}\n}}\n{{Infobox handball club|\nclubname= RK Vogo\u0161\u0107a|\n| image = |\n| founded = |\n| fullname = Rukometni klub Vogo\u0161\u0107a|\n| ground = Sportska Dvorana Amel Be\u010dkovi\u0107\n| capacity =  |            \n| chairman =  |\n| manager = / |\n| league = [[Handball Championship of Bosnia and Herzegovina|Premijer Liga]] |\n| season = 2017-18 |\n| position = 2nd |\n| website     = http://rkvogosca-poljinehills.ba/ |}}\n\n'''RK Vogo\u0161\u0107a Poljine Hills''' is a [[Bosnia and Herzegovina|Bosnian]] [[Team handball|handball]] team located in [[Vogo\u0161\u0107a]]. Their home matches are played at Sportska Dvorana Amel Be\u010dkovi\u0107. They compete in [[Handball Championship of Bosnia and Herzegovina]] where their best result is 2nd in 2015-2016.\n\n== Accomplishments ==\n\n* [[Handball Championship of Bosnia and Herzegovina|Premijer Liga]]\n** '''Runner-Up (2)''' : 2016, 2018\n\n==European record ==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Season\n! Competition\n! Round\n! Club\n! 1st leg\n! 2nd leg\n! Aggregate\n|-\n| colspan=\"7\" bgcolor=white|\n|-\n| [[2016\u201317 EHF Challenge Cup|2016\u201317]]\n| [[EHF Challenge Cup|Challenge Cup]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[2016\u201317 EHF Challenge Cup#Round 3|R3]]\n| {{flagicon|MKD}} [[RK Pelister]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 23\u201321\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 25\u201328\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| '''48\u201349'''\n|}\n\n== Team ==\n\n=== Current squad ===\n\n:''Squad for the 2016\u201317 season''\n{{Col-begin|width=60%}}\n{{Col-2}}\n;Goalkeepers\n*{{flagicon|BIH}} Ismar Had\u017ei\u0107\n*{{flagicon|BIH}} Mirza Haselji\u0107 \n*{{flagicon|BIH}} Adnan \u0160abanovi\u0107\n\n;Wingers\n;RW:\n* {{flagicon|BIH}} Anes Be\u010di\u0107 \n* {{flagicon|BIH}} Adi D\u017einovi\u0107\n* {{flagicon|BIH}} Medin \u0160estan\n;LW: \n* {{flagicon|BIH}} Ibro Jela\u010di